The time for sunrise and sunset from 90 degree in am and pm. +ve above the horizon, -ve below the horizon.

Source: R/functionLibrary.R
sunRiseSet.Rd

The time for sunrise and sunset from 90 degree in am and pm. +ve above the horizon, -ve below the horizon.

sunRiseSet(doy, lat, long, timezone = 0, angle = 6, flag = "rise")

Arguments

doy

day of year number
lat

latitude of site (deg)
long

longitude of site (deg)
timezone

local time
angle

angle to measure time between, such as twilight (deg). angular distance between 90 deg and end of twilight - altitude of sun. +ve up, -ve down.
flag

rise or set
